<plot>Lap takes place at a bus stop where a series of encounters between a man and a woman unfolds on rainy nights. Returning to the same bus stop every night the film follows Lula as she meets Alan. On the surface there is nothing unusual in their meeting. Slowly however Lula finds herself drawn to Alan - his sense of humour and body movements fascinate her. But is he to be trusted?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?319179</url></doc>
